The **Plan-Do-Check-Act cycle** really resonates with me. Too often, orgs â€œset and forgetâ€ their security. I believe real resilience comes from **ongoing review and adaptation** â€” especially in fast-changing fields like healthcare IT. If I were leading a security program, Iâ€™d prioritize **continuous tuning** of controls to stay ahead of emerging threats.

